snippet.title: The Disney Afternoon Collection - Darkwing Duck Retrospective
snippet.description:
It's go time! Let's see what Darkwing Duck is all about and how his superhero gadgets translated into the 8-bit classic!

Darwking Duck is just one of the six games featured in The Disney Afternoon Collection, available now for PC, Xbox One and PlayStation 4. http://bit.ly/2oJIDpk

Subscribe to the Official Capcom Unity Channel: 
http://bit.ly/Qjb2MV
